@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

title Data Mesh - Runtime Connectivity and Service Interactions

actor User
participant "SQLPad\n(SQL IDE)" as SQLPad
participant "Consul\n(Service Discovery)" as Consul
participant "Consul Connect\nSidecar Proxy" as ProxySQLPad
participant "Consul Connect\nSidecar Proxy" as ProxyPresto
participant "Presto\n(Query Engine)" as Presto
participant "Consul Connect\nSidecar Proxy" as ProxyHive
participant "Hive Metastore\n(Metadata)" as Hive
participant "Consul Connect\nSidecar Proxy" as ProxyMinio
participant "MinIO\n(Object Storage)" as MinIO
participant "Nomad\n(Orchestrator)" as Nomad

== Service Registration and Discovery ==

Nomad -> MinIO : Deploy MinIO Service
activate MinIO
MinIO -> ProxyMinio : Start Sidecar Proxy
activate ProxyMinio
ProxyMinio -> Consul : Register MinIO Service
activate Consul
Consul --> ProxyMinio : Registration Confirmed
deactivate Consul

Nomad -> Hive : Deploy Hive Metastore
activate Hive
Hive -> ProxyHive : Start Sidecar Proxy
activate ProxyHive
ProxyHive -> Consul : Register Hive Service
activate Consul
Consul --> ProxyHive : Registration Confirmed

Nomad -> Presto : Deploy Presto Query Engine
activate Presto
Presto -> ProxyPresto : Start Sidecar Proxy
activate ProxyPresto
ProxyPresto -> Consul : Register Presto Service
Consul --> ProxyPresto : Registration Confirmed

Nomad -> SQLPad : Deploy SQLPad
activate SQLPad
SQLPad -> ProxySQLPad : Start Sidecar Proxy
activate ProxySQLPad
ProxySQLPad -> Consul : Register SQLPad Service
Consul --> ProxySQLPad : Registration Confirmed
deactivate Consul

== Health Check Monitoring ==

Nomad -> MinIO : Health Check
MinIO --> Nomad : Health Status OK
Nomad -> Hive : Health Check
Hive --> Nomad : Health Status OK
Nomad -> Presto : Health Check
Presto --> Nomad : Health Status OK
Nomad -> SQLPad : Health Check
SQLPad --> Nomad : Health Status OK

== Query Execution Flow ==

User -> SQLPad : Submit SQL Query
SQLPad -> Consul : Discover Presto Service
activate Consul
Consul --> SQLPad : Presto Service Location
deactivate Consul

SQLPad -> ProxySQLPad : Query Request (via Consul Connect)
ProxySQLPad -> ProxySQLPad : mTLS Authentication
ProxySQLPad -> ProxyPresto : Encrypted Request
ProxyPresto -> ProxyPresto : mTLS Verification
ProxyPresto -> Presto : Forward Query

Presto -> Consul : Discover Hive Metastore
activate Consul
Consul --> Presto : Hive Service Location
deactivate Consul

Presto -> ProxyPresto : Request Schema Metadata
ProxyPresto -> ProxyHive : Encrypted Request (via Consul Connect)
ProxyHive -> ProxyHive : mTLS Verification
ProxyHive -> Hive : Get Table Schema

Hive -> ProxyHive : Return Schema Metadata
ProxyHive -> ProxyPresto : Encrypted Response
ProxyPresto -> Presto : Schema Information

Presto -> Consul : Discover MinIO Service
activate Consul
Consul --> Presto : MinIO Service Location
deactivate Consul

Presto -> ProxyPresto : Request Data from Storage
ProxyPresto -> ProxyMinio : Encrypted Request (via Consul Connect)
ProxyMinio -> ProxyMinio : mTLS Verification
ProxyMinio -> MinIO : S3-compatible API Call

MinIO -> ProxyMinio : Return Data
ProxyMinio -> ProxyPresto : Encrypted Response
ProxyPresto -> Presto : Data Stream

Presto -> Presto : Process Query & Execute
Presto -> ProxyPresto : Query Results
ProxyPresto -> ProxySQLPad : Encrypted Response
ProxySQLPad -> SQLPad : Results

SQLPad -> User : Display Query Results

== Service-to-Service Secure Communication Pattern ==

note over ProxySQLPad, ProxyMinio
All service-to-service communication flows through
Consul Connect sidecar proxies with mutual TLS (mTLS)
for authentication, authorization, and encryption
end note

deactivate MinIO
deactivate ProxyMinio
deactivate Hive
deactivate ProxyHive
deactivate Presto
deactivate ProxyPresto
deactivate SQLPad
deactivate ProxySQLPad

@enduml
